./hellminer --help

Usage: hellminer [options]

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -l, --list            list available OpenCL devices by ID (GPUs...)
  --cpu=CPU             run N threads of Verushash on CPU (default: 1)
  --gpu=LIST            use specified GPU device IDs to mine, for example to
                        use the first three: 0,1,2 (default: 0)
  --instances=N         run N instances of Verushash per Solver (default: 1)
  -c POOL, --connect=POOL
                        example stratum+tcp://example.com:1234 (add "#xnsub"
                        to enable extranonce.subscribe)
  -u USER, --user=USER  username for connecting to the pool
  -p PWD, --pwd=PWD     password for connecting to the pool
  -v, --verbose         verbose mode (may be repeated for more verbosity)
  --debug               enable debug mode (for developers only)
